3.  Attributes and Variables                                 Command Reference
                route.detail.generate_extra_off_grid_pin_tracks

NAME
       route.detail.generate_extra_off_grid_pin_tracks
              Specifies  whether to generate extra off-grid routing tracks for
              pin connections. If set to true, the  router  more  aggressively
              generates off-grid dynamic tracks.

TYPE
       Boolean

DEFAULT
       false

DESCRIPTION
       This  application  option  specifies whether to generate extra off-grid
       routing tracks for pin connections.

SEE ALSO
